name: LOFT256
description: V4w.enko - "LOFT256" is one more component. The form is based on spherical voronoi tessellation and extrude of centers of segments with one loft.  The structure shows the whole energy of the archetype which is used for the next step of creation.  The GLB 3D object type allows Augmented Reality mode to zoom, pan, rotate to see more perspectives.
